query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `installation_steps` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `inspection_item_id` int NOT NULL,
  `step_name` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `step_order` int NOT NULL,
  `is_completed` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `completed_at` timestamp NULL,
  `notes` text,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `installation_steps_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `installation_steps_inspection_item_id_inspection_items_id_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`inspection_item_id`) REFERENCES `inspection_items`(`id`) ON DELETE cascade ON UPDATE no action
);
